{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-180-rational-zeros-of-a-function-of-three-variables","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","demoType":null,"title":"Izazov 180: Pozitivna racionalna rešenja funkcije od tri promenljive","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Za svaki ceo broj $n$, razmotri tri funkcije</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; f_{1,n}(x,y,z) = x^{n + 1} + y^{n + 1} − z^{n + 1}\\\\\n&#x26; f_{2,n}(x,y,z) = (xy + yz + zx) \\times (x^{n - 1} + y^{n - 1} − z^{n - 1})\\\\\n&#x26; f_{3,n}(x,y,z) = xyz \\times (x^{n - 2} + y^{n - 2} − z^{n - 2})\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>na mchanganyiko wao</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; f_n(x,y,z) = f_{1,n}(x,y,z) + f_{2,n}(x,y,z) − f_{3,n}(x,y,z)\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>Trojku $(x,y,z)$ nazivamo zlatnom trojkom reda $k$ ako su $x$, $y$ i $z$ pozitivni racionalni brojevi oblika $\\frac{a}{b}$, gde važi $0 &#x3C; a &#x3C; b ≤ k$, i postoji (najmanje jedan) ceo broj $n$ takav da je $f_n(x,y,z) = 0$.</p>\n<p>Acha $s(x,y,z) = x + y + z$.</p>\n<p>Neka je $t = \\frac{u}{v}$ zbir svih različitih vrednosti $s(x,y,z)$ za sve zlatne trojke $(x,y,z)$ reda 35. I $s(x,y,z)$ i $t$ moraju biti zapisani u skraćenom obliku.</p>\n<p>Tafuta $u + v$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4201000cf542c50ff33","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301816,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-180-rational-zeros-of-a-function-of-three-variables"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function rationalZeros() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nrationalZeros();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],